ZH: 四个人去看电影。
EN: Four people went to see a movie.

ZH: 这本书分成四个部分。
EN: This book is divided into four parts.

ZH: 我已经学会了四种不同的语言。
EN: I have learned four different languages.

ZH: 我家有四只猫。
EN: There are four cats in my house.

ZH: 在这个城市有四个季节。
EN: There are four seasons in this city.

ZH: 这个星期有四天上班。
EN: There are four working days this week.

ZH: 我家离学校只有四公里。
EN: My house is only four kilometers away from the school.

ZH: 孩子们在教室里坐着，一排四个人。
EN: The children are sitting in rows of four in the classroom.

ZH: 我的家乡有四个著名的景点。
EN: There are four famous attractions in my hometown.

ZH: 过去的四年里，我们取得了很多进步。
EN: We have made a lot of progress in the past four years.

ZH: 这个问题有四个不同的解决方案。
EN: There are four different solutions to this problem.

ZH: 这次旅行我们有四个人一起去。
EN: There are four people going on this trip with us.

ZH: 那个表演持续了四个小时。
EN: That performance lasted for four hours.

ZH: 我已经戒烟四年了。
EN: I have quit smoking for four years.

ZH: 上个月我买了四本新书。
EN: I bought four new books last month.

ZH: 昨天我去超市买了四袋米。
EN: I bought four bags of rice at the supermarket yesterday.

ZH: 这个城市有四座大桥。
EN: There are four big bridges in this city.

ZH: 我昨晚睡了四个小时。
EN: I slept for four hours last night.

ZH: 我去买菜，你去付四个人的账。
EN: I'll go buy groceries, you go pay for the four people's bill.

ZH: 我一口气喝掉了四杯咖啡。
EN: I drank four cups of coffee in one gulp.
